            <bug_when>2009-10-16 10:38:43 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>There is no generic fix thor this issue. To solve this issue in an application one of the scrollbars has to be visible all the time:

e.g.

iframe.setScrollbarX(&quot;on&quot;)

or

iframe.setScrollbarY(&quot;on&quot;)</thetext>
